{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/bealka-steam-10b.gif?t=1736775773\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A desperate letter summons detective Paul Trilby to a peculiar island town, divided by a wall and ruled by a Hospital. Regular citizens get admitted and then return without their memories. A sinister conspiracy is afoot. Can you get to the bottom of this mystery?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the meaning is a surreal, hand-drawn, point-and-click adventure inspired by classic titles like Samorost and the Rusty Lake series.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/steambanner_2.gif?t=1736775773\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use wit, curiosity and lateral thinking to puzzle your way towards a solution, helped by the citizens you meet along the way. Remember that there is always a grain of truth in the local gossip. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/short-adventure_05.gif?t=1736775773\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short, strange, satisfying adventure for those in search of something different. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25a0 Hand-drawn art brings the offbeat world to life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25a0 Whimsical worldbuilding with a sinister undertone</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25a0 Atmospheric soundtrack by Victor Butzelaar</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25a0 A twisted mystery that awaits your diligent inspection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25a0 1.5 hours average playtime<br><br>\ud83d\udd0e You can already start <i>Paul_Trilby</i>'s investigation by visiting the